
Requirements:

1. create post API end point called addBlog, which should take
blogname, blogid, blog description and blog image url.

note: display data in console.

2. create get API end point called getPosts, which should return
a list of posts . 

note: return an array of posts as part of response.

3. create get API end point called getPost/id, which should 
return a specific post.

note: you need to use the following url

htpp://localhost:portno/getPost/1

